# Sample API Requests for Payment Enrichment Service

## Enrich Single Transaction

POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/enrichment/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "txn-demo-001",
  "merchantId": "merch-12345",
  "merchantName": "Starbucks Coffee",
  "amount": 5.75,
  "currency": "USD",
  "country": "Canada",
  "city": "Vancouver",
  "latitude": 49.2827,
  "longitude": -123.1207
}

###

